channel.title: L33tpwnzscape [317] release
channel.description:
[center][size=24pt]V2 has been released! [color=blue]V2 link: [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,467730.msg3419781.html#msg3419781]http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,467730.msg3419781.html#msg3419781[/url][/color][/size][/center]
This is my first release so please leave some constructive criticism and not leech off of my hard work :P
If you use this to make your server, please pm me so I can take a look at it. Wouldn't mind you giving me an owner spot if I decide to play it ;) ;)
[left][size=18pt]L33tpwnzscape v1 release![/size][/left]
[center]Barrows[/center] [center]Working DFS[/center] [center]Pest control with void knight armor rewards[/center] [center]Fight pits and fight caves(7 waves)[/center] [center]All skills work![/center] [center]That's all I can think of but theres much more!!![/center]
Working dragon claw special! [img]http://i818.photobucket.com/albums/zz108/yelser1/l33tpwnzscape/workingdclawspec.jpg?t=1282324749[/img]
Use d bones on altar for prayer xp! [img]http://i818.photobucket.com/albums/zz108/yelser1/l33tpwnzscape/usingbonesonaltar.jpg?t=1282324749[/img]
Corp beast!! [img]http://i818.photobucket.com/albums/zz108/yelser1/l33tpwnzscape/ScreenShot.jpg?t=1282324749[/img]
Spirit shield drops [img]http://i818.photobucket.com/albums/zz108/yelser1/l33tpwnzscape/spiritshielddrops.jpg?t=1282324749[/img]
Working slayer assignments [img]http://i818.photobucket.com/albums/zz108/yelser1/l33tpwnzscape/slayer.jpg?t=1282324749[/img]
Skilling area [img]http://i818.photobucket.com/albums/zz108/yelser1/l33tpwnzscape/skillarea.jpg?t=1282324749[/img]
Quest tab has teleports, rules and commands [img]http://i818.photobucket.com/albums/zz108/yelser1/l33tpwnzscape/questtab.jpg?t=1282324749[/img]
Pk point exchange shop [img]http://i818.photobucket.com/albums/zz108/yelser1/l33tpwnzscape/pkpexhangeshop.jpg?t=1282324749[/img]
New whip graphic! [img]http://i818.photobucket.com/albums/zz108/yelser1/l33tpwnzscape/newwhipgraphic.jpg?t=1282324749[/img]
Home [img]http://i818.photobucket.com/albums/zz108/yelser1/l33tpwnzscape/home.jpg?t=1282324749[/img]
Godsword stance [img]http://i818.photobucket.com/albums/zz108/yelser1/l33tpwnzscape/gsstance.jpg[/img]
Donator area [img]http://i818.photobucket.com/albums/zz108/yelser1/l33tpwnzscape/donatorarea.jpg?t=1282325126[/img]
Known bugs: -Auto retaliate doesn't work when fighting npcs for some reason. -1 error with the client which I can't figure out how to fix. -Ancients don't freeze the enemy.
Source: [url=http://uppit.com/0srevm315jxi/l33tpwnzscape_source.rar]http://uppit.com/0srevm315jxi/l33tpwnzscape_source.rar[/url]
Client: [url=http://uppit.com/nisoix8flb91/l33tpwnzscape_client.rar]http://uppit.com/nisoix8flb91/l33tpwnzscape_client.rar[/url]
Hope you like it :) Enjoy!
Creds: EvolutionXscape(source)-60% Me(heavy modifying and editing)-40%

item.dc:creator: @wetodded wetodded
item.description:
@wetodded wrote:

[quote=“yelser, post:74, topic:356025”]if you want to see a server without all the features i have, then why are you criticizing this? is a runescape private server. they’re all the same.

idiots…[/quote]

    That's the dumbest thing I have ever heard. If that's the case why the fuck did you even attempt to create a server? In your logic, if they are all the same, then you sir, have wasted your time. No one wants to see the same shit posted 100 times on this section of the forums. It's the same features, different namnes. Don't get me wrong, there are awesome servers out there. However, this "type" of server has been overdone and is a waste to the community and a waste of your time. I'm being honest and trying to help you. Just STOP, or... Think of something new that hasn't been done before. I feel asthough I could look on my HD and find a server with the same features from 2 years ago.
